This paper presents a framework for using diverse suboptimal world models to decompose complex task solutions into simpler modular subpolicies, which involves techniques from machine learning, artificial intelligence, robotics, and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
